All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Asteroid
The Asteroid interface is used to create asteroids and spawn asteroids.
Asteroid
The Asteroid class creates the asteroids and the big asteroids.
Asteroids
The Asteroids class creates Arraylist for asteroids and big asteroids.
BigAsteroid
The BigAsteroid class creates the big asteroids.
Bullet
The Bullet interface is used to fire the bullets.
Bullet
The Bullet class creates the bullets.
Collision
The Collision class is an abstract class that is used to check for collisions
Collisions
The Collisions class checks for collisions between the weapons and the asteroids.
GameStage
The GameStage class creates the game stage.
HelloApplication
The HelloApplication class is the main class of the application.
HelloController
HelloController is the controller class for the main menu.
IAsteroids<T>
The IAsteroids interface is used to add asteroids and big asteroids.
MusicPlayer
The MusicPlayer class plays the music and the sound effects.
NormalAsteroid
NormalAsteroid class is used to create normal asteroids.
OptionsController
The optionscontroller class is responsible for the options page.
Player
The Player class creates the player.
SecondStageController
The secondstagecontroller class is responsible for the second page of the main menu.
Space
The Space class creates the background of the game.
Velocity
The Velocity class controls the speed of the asteroids.
